name: Mr.Bijan
description:
6 days ago, autumn began in Iran.
We have not yet worn our warm clothes and scarves.
but bijan wearing hoodie.
we call him Autumn Man.
Bijan recites poetry in the fall
He walks in the streets and feeds the birds.
he talk to the trees while holding a cup of coffee.
Bijan sleeps in other seasons and only wakes up in autumn.
That's why I call him Autumn Man !!!
